Gourmet Pickle and Cheese Plate

10 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Description

A delightful assortment of tangy pickles and creamy cheeses, perfect for snacking or entertaining.

Ingredients

  • assorted pickles: 1 cup
  • cheddar cheese: 100 grams
  • gouda cheese: 100 grams
  • brie cheese: 100 grams
  • crackers: 1 box
  • olives: 1/2 cup
  • fresh grapes: 1 cup
